# Declarations

## Basics

Declaring a primitive or an object is quite straight forward:
```gwion,editable
var int i;
var Object o;
<<< i, " ", o >>>;
```

## Declaring a reference

```gwion,editable
late Object object_ref;
<<< "Reference points to no object yet: ", object_ref >>>;
new Object => object_ref;
<<< "But now it does: ", object_ref >>>;
```

## Arrays

### array as refs

```gwion,editable
var int array_ref[];
<<< array_ref >>>;
new int[2] => array_ref;
<<< array_ref >>>;
```
